      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready for your dream ride? I\u2019m parting with this absolute beauty and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels just like it rolled off the lot! It has been totally pampered since day one, always kept in the garage, and it drives like an absolute dream. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup here. Come take a look and see for yourself, you're going to fall in love with it!",
