    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely no swirls, stone chips, or imperfections across the laser-straight body panels. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and free of creases, with every electronic component and switch functioning exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, it is flawless; the engine bay is spotless, and the service records are comprehensive, documenting a life of meticulous preventative maintenance. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a showroom-quality example that drives as perfectly as it looks. No accidents, no smoke, and no stories\u2014just pure, preserved quality.",
